data.description: Welcome home to this 3/ 2 gated community located in the desirable Tamaya neighborhood.  This beautiful one story features plenty of premium living space.  The large high ceiling family room is centrally located for maximum convenience. A spacious gourmet kitchen and dining area are perfect for entertaining.  Going out the 3 slider door leads to the closed in screened and Vinyl window lanai with outdoor kitchen.  The main suite is placed at the rear of the home for peace and quiet.  Two more sperate bedrooms with a full spacious bathroom. Enjoy the back yard with additional pavers and Pergola. You will love making this home your own.  Great location to all shopping.  Beautiful Amenities.  Just minutes to Mayo Clinic, I-295 and the beaches. Location, Location, Location!  Welcome Home!
